description: “Nor have [women] been ashamed to put their tender white hands to mechanical things, and amid the coarseness of marble and the roughness of iron to follow their desires and bring fame to themselves, as did our Properzia de’ Rossi, a young woman talented not only in household matters, but in infinite forms of knowledge that are the envy of men as well as women.” Relief sculpture digitally traced and hand-altered. Minted for Objkt4objkt 23 April 2021
